| [{{fr_id}}.AC2](#{{fr_anchor}}ac2---edge-or-alternate-path) | Edge or alternate path | TBD alternate valid condition, boundary case, or partial data state. | TBD actor or system performs the alternate action. | TBD expected alternate outcome without ambiguity. |
| [{{fr_id}}.AC3](#{{fr_anchor}}ac3---error-permission-or-exception-path) | Error, permission, or exception path | TBD invalid, unauthorized, duplicate, missing, upstream-failure, unsupported, or timeout condition. | TBD actor or system attempts the action. | TBD rejection, error message, rollback/no-change rule, audit entry, retry path, or escalation behavior. |

